    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80e8-b18b-d5f56e7e0de2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "KT is a popular application of LA research and, nowadays, there are increasingly more student representations who are becoming increasingly complex. However, most approaches are inneficient at updating the learner’s knowledge state, often leading to poor predictions. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-80e8-b18b-d5f56e7e0de2",
