      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-8044-a99f-c70d34166d14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors employ a causal inference model to explain KT. The idea stems from the construcion of balanced weights for the different features. Experimentation on different datasets shows that model is accurate and interpretable (2 hallmarks for good KT models.",
